description:
hi !! i'am kasraoui mohamed hedi and i'am a mechanical engineer.

i use every day catia v5 , part design workbench is very important for CAD designers to know much about it , because it allows the designers to transform 2D sketchs to 3D models with severals methods.

this course is for all levels : beginners , intermediate , and advanced catia v5 users.

after taking this course you will be able to design 3d models using the most advanced features of catia v5 part design workbench like : dress up features , sketch based features , transformation features and other features.

best regards.

K.M.H | mechanical engineer.
title: the most powerful 50 tools of catia v5 part design
